OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMainly clear
OL,6,Fskies to start the evening, becoming
OL,7,Fcloudy at times especially along the
OL,8,Fcoast and across the entire region by
OL,9,Fdawn, perhaps some light rain near the
OL,10,FNorfolk coast. Winds light north-
OL,11,Fwesterly but breezy along the coast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FA cloudy morning perhaps with
OL,14,Fsome light rain near the Norfolk
OL,15,Fcoast. Cloud breaking through the late
OL,16,Fmorning and afternoon with some sunny
OL,17,Fspells developing. Winds mainly light
OL,18,Fand variable.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
